+/*
+ * This file is an awful patch/workaround for Android. It looks like
+ * link.h is missing from the Android definition (only elf.h is provided)
+ * and thus some structure definitions are lacking. This file defines them.
+ * This file is actually a bunch of several cut-and-pasts from Linux link.h
+ * file. It must _ABSOLUTELY_ be double checked by someone familiar with
+ * the ELF format and Android (which is not my (MS) case).
+ *
+ * Even less than the other file, this one is distributed with absolutely
+ * no warranty at all because I (MS again) don't really understand what I'm
+ * doing. You have been warned...
